<header>
    <div class="logo"> uFlu? </div>
    <span id="header-message">{{rquote}}</span>
</header>

<div id="container-fluid" class="desk-bg">

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 clearfix">

            <div class="result-message1">
                <div class="message-logo">uFlu? </div>
                <div class="result-text1">Hi <span id="user-name">{{name}}</span>, <br>
                    Based on your symptoms, you might have <span id="diagnosis-result">{{severity}}.</span> <br>
                    Below is a list of suggestions to help you feel more comfortable:<br>
                    <span id="items">{{#each cureList}}<li>{{this}}</li>{{/each}}</span>

                    Here is a <a href="http://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?data=uFlu%3F%20Shopping%20List%3A%20%7C%20Cough%20Drops%20%7C%20Facial%20Tissue%20%7C%20Hand%20Sanitizer%20%7C%20Decongestant%20%7C%20Pain%20Reliever&size=100x100"></a>
                    link to a list of shopping items for you.

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="result-message2">
                <div class="result-text2">
                    We suggest that you get some medication. Here is a list:<br>
                    <span id="items">{{#each medicineList}}<li>{{this}}</li>{{/each}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="result-message3">
                <div class="result-text3">
                    Here is a map to some pharmacies in your area. <iframe id="location-map" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/search?q=pharmacy&&zoom=13&key=AIzaSyCBAUrhIbvz3xZoeo5--j9mFDf-Zpo8EC8"
                        allowfullscreen></iframe>
                    <br>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="result-message4">
                <div class="result-text4">
                    Also, if you can't contact your family doctor, try <a href="https://www.teladoc.com/" id="teladoc-link"
                        target="blank">Teladoc</a>.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="result-icons">
                <div class="pad-holder"></div>
                <div class="pen"><img scr="/img/pen.png" /></div>
                <div class="pencil"><img scr="../public/img/pencil.png" /></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer>

        </footer>

    </div>

</div>

</div>